sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(SDK / Dashboard)
    participant APIServer as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL / PostgreSQL<br/>3306/TCP or 5432/TCP
    participant ObjStore as Object Store<br/>(MinIO / S3 / GCS)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>Engine
    participant Driver as Driver<br/>(init container)
    participant MLMD as MLMD Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher<br/>(main container)
    participant PAgent as Persistence Agent
    participant SWFCtrl as SWF Controller<br/>9090/TCP metrics

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,PAgent: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Submission
        Client->>APIServer: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Bearer Token (Optional TLS)
        APIServer->>DB: Persist run metadata<br/>Username/Password (Optional TLS)
        APIServer->>ObjStore: Store pipeline spec<br/>Static API keys (TLS 1.2+)
        APIServer->>K8sAPI: Create Argo Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount (TLS in-cluster)

        K8sAPI->>Argo: Schedule workflow execution

        Argo->>Driver: Run as init step (local process)
        Driver->>MLMD: Resolve execution context<br/>gRPC (Optional TLS)
        Driver->>APIServer: Cache check via TaskService<br/>gRPC 8887 (Optional TLS)
        Driver-->>Argo: Pod spec patch written

        Argo->>Launcher: Run as main container (local process)
        Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution outputs<br/>gRPC (Optional TLS)
        Launcher->>ObjStore: Upload output artifacts<br/>Kubernetes Secret (TLS 1.2+)
        Launcher-->>Argo: Task complete

        PAgent->>K8sAPI: Watch Workflow status<br/>ServiceAccount (TLS in-cluster)
        PAgent->>APIServer: Report run status<br/>HTTP 8888 Bearer Token (Optional TLS)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,SWFCtrl: Flow 2: Scheduled Workflow Execution
        Client->>APIServer: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>Bearer Token (Optional TLS)
        APIServer->>K8sAPI: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount (TLS in-cluster)
        SWFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch ScheduledWorkflow<br/>ServiceAccount (TLS in-cluster)
        SWFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Argo Workflow on schedule<br/>ServiceAccount (TLS in-cluster)
        SWFCtrl->>APIServer: Create run record<br/>gRPC 8887 Bearer Token (Optional TLS)
    end
